Design a premium enterprise-grade “Supplier Data Ingestion & Intelligence Workspace” for HSBC Sustainable Transition Copilot.

IMPORTANT:
This is NOT an ESG dashboard.

This is:
- a supplier sustainability intelligence ingestion platform
- a fragmented enterprise data unification system
- an AI-assisted operational data orchestration layer

The goal of this experience is:
- connect fragmented enterprise systems
- ingest supplier operational data
- unify supplier records
- build supplier profiles
- prepare sustainability intelligence pipelines

DO NOT focus on analytics or charts yet.

The UI should primarily communicate:
“Connect systems → ingest fragmented supplier data → unify supplier intelligence.”

