==================================================
CONNECTOR GRID
==================================================

Group connectors into categories.

--------------------------------------------------
CATEGORY 1 — PROCUREMENT & OPERATIONS
--------------------------------------------------

Cards:
- Outlook
- SharePoint
- SAP
- Oracle
- Excel
- Google Sheets

Each connector card includes:
- connector icon
- short operational description
- type of supplier data accessible
- security indicator
- Connect button

Example:
OUTLOOK

Description:
Access supplier invoices, procurement conversations, logistics attachments, and operational documents.

Data Types:
- invoices
- quotations
- logistics bills
- procurement communication

Button:
[ Connect Securely ]

--------------------------------------------------
CATEGORY 2 — CLOUD STORAGE
--------------------------------------------------

Cards:
- Google Drive
- OneDrive
- Dropbox

Descriptions:
Access ESG reports, utility bills, procurement files, and supplier documents stored across shared drives.

--------------------------------------------------
CATEGORY 3 — COMMUNICATION CHANNELS
--------------------------------------------------

Cards:
- WhatsApp Business
- Teams
- Telegram

Descriptions:
Ingest invoice images, shipment confirmations, operational updates, and supplier communication records.

--------------------------------------------------
CATEGORY 4 — MANUAL IMPORTS
--------------------------------------------------

Cards:
- PDF Upload
- CSV Upload
- Excel Upload
- Image Upload

